briefdescription.para: Convert an interval to half tone based pitch according to MIDI pitch numbers.

detaileddescription.para: The microtonal part is retained in the double return value.

parameterdescription.para: Interval in the internal representation of Mutabor.

simplesect.para: a double value that represents the interval. a half tone is represented as 1.00, and an octave as 12.00.

briefdescription.para: Convert an interval from half tone based pitch according to MIDI pitch numbers.

detaileddescription.para: The microtonal part can be given in the double value.

parameterdescription.para: a double value that represents the interval. a semitone is represented as 1.00, and an octave as 12.00

simplesect.para: interval in the internal representation of Mutabor.

briefdescription.para: Convert a tone to half tone based pitch according to MIDI pitch numbers.

detaileddescription.para: The microtonal part is retained in the double return value.

parameterdescription.para: Interval in the internal representation of Mutabor.

simplesect.para: a double value that represents the tone a' is represented as 69.00

briefdescription.para: Convert a tone from half tone based pitch according to MIDI pitch numbers.

detaileddescription.para: The microtonal part can be given in the double value.

parameterdescription.para: a double value that represents the tone. a' is represented as 69.00

simplesect.para: tone in the internal representation of Mutabor.

briefdescription.para: Interpreter for the logic at runtime.
